title: War of the Roses: The Starbucks Cup
description: Kayla saw that her boyfriend Geoff had a Starbucks cup with the name Lydia written on it.  When she asked him about he, he said he just grabbed the wrong drink.  But then she got a very weird text from a random number about her boyfriend so she is not trusting that he "grabbed the wrong drink".
